title: International Parking Management (IPM)
description: Specializing in innovative, customer-centered parking solutions, this Seattle-based, family-owned company has thrived for over 36 years by offering exceptional service and ensuring maximum growth and profitability for commercial, retail, and residential properties.

title: Metropolis - Checkout-Free Parking with AI
description: Revolutionizing urban parking, the platform leverages computer vision for seamless, checkout-free transactions, enhancing convenience for drivers and boosting revenue for property owners across major metropolitan areas.
